msgstr ""
"Odoo Firma garantisce la piena conformità alla legge sulla firma elettronica "
"del Regno Unito incorporando le seguenti caratteristiche:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/validity/united_kingdom.rst:62
msgid ""
"While Odoo Sign is broadly applicable, there are certain exceptions where "
"electronic signatures may not be suitable or legally recognized in the "
"United Kingdom:"
msgstr ""
"Sebbene Odoo Firma sia ampiamente applicabile, esistono alcune eccezioni in "
"cui le firme elettroniche potrebbero non essere adatte o legalmente "
"riconosciute nel Regno Unito:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/validity/united_kingdom.rst:73
msgid ""
"The information provided on this page is for general informational purposes "
"only and does not constitute legal advice. While Odoo Sign complies with the "
"Electronic Signature Law of the United Kingdom, users should consult with "
"legal professionals to ensure specific document types and use cases meet all "
"legal requirements. Compliance with additional industry-specific regulations "
"may also be necessary."
msgstr ""
"Le informazioni fornite in questa pagina sono solo a scopo informativo "
"generale e non costituiscono consulenza legale. Sebbene Odoo Firma sia "
